					<h2 style="text-align:left; font-size:26px;">
					<span style="color: #449CCC;">Food and Nutrition</span>
					</h2>
					<p style="text-align: justify;"> SCHOOL MEALS</p>
					<p>The food programme is one of our key projects. It has helped vulnerable children in their health, growth, weights, nutrition and well-being. The food programme operates from our Anganza School and is carried out by our school cook and volunteers. Meals are cooked with a combination of ingredients including beans, maize, cereals, rice and locally grown vegetables.</p>

