					<h2 style="text-align:left; font-size:26px;">
					<span style="color: #449CCC;">Education</span>
					</h2>
					<p style="text-align: justify;"> LEARNING AND GROWING</p>
					<p>Children in our community love going to school! De’ Bridge community centre runs an Early Childhood Development (ECD) School for children aged 3-7 and a senior school currently up to form 2. This programme is a gateway for children to enter the education system. Once a child has moved through the ECD School they are then enrolled into a public primary school, where they will spend the next eight years. With the support of child sponsors De’ bridge community centre supports children through their senior school education.</p>

				</div>

